Two leg logic
Find all destinations of A
Find all origins of C
Find location that is on destination of A and origin of C

Three leg logic
Method 1:
Find all destinations of A
Find all origins of D
Find leg with destination of A and origin of D
Method 2:
Find all destinations of A
Find all destinations of destinations of A
Find destination of destinations of of destinations of A that equals D

Four leg logic
Find all destinations of A
Find all destinations of destinations of A
Find all destinations of all destinations of all destinations of A
Find destination of all destinations of all destinations of all destinations of A that equals E

